{"article_id":"6JBks55LyuNfJFQa","edus":[{"id":0,"text":"The `` Harry Potter '' author has come under fire","depth":6},{"id":1,"text":"for tweeting a message of support Thursday for Maya Forstater , a researcher","depth":8},{"id":2,"text":"who lost her job at a think tank","depth":8},{"id":3,"text":"for stating","depth":8},{"id":4,"text":"that people can not change their biological sex .","depth":8},{"id":5,"text":"`` Dress however you please , ''","depth":8},{"id":6,"text":"Rowling wrote .","depth":8},{"id":7,"text":"`` Call yourself whatever you like .","depth":9},{"id":8,"text":"Sleep with any consenting adult","depth":11},{"id":9,"text":"who ' ll have you .","depth":11},{"id":10,"text":"Live your best life in peace and security .","depth":10},{"id":11,"text":"But force women out of their jobs","depth":9},{"id":12,"text":"for stating","depth":10},{"id":13,"text":"that sex is real ?","depth":10},{"id":14,"text":"# IStandWithMaya","depth":7},{"id":15,"text":"# ThisIsNotADrill ''","depth":7},{"id":16,"text":"The \" Harry Potter \" author ,","depth":7},{"id":17,"text":"otherwise known for her liberal political views ,","depth":7},{"id":18,"text":"was label by many on Twitter as a TERF","depth":7},{"id":19,"text":"( Trans Exclusive Radical Feminist ) .","depth":7},{"id":20,"text":"The hashtag `` # JKRowlingIsATerf '' was a top trending topic that day .","depth":5},{"id":21,"text":"A spokesperson for Rowling told","depth":4},{"id":22,"text":"the author would not have any further comment .","depth":4},{"id":23,"text":"The researcher was a visiting fellow at the Centre for Global Development ,","depth":5},{"id":24,"text":"which in March declined to renew her contract .","depth":5},{"id":25,"text":"A London judge this week upheld her dismissal ,","depth":7},{"id":26,"text":"finding","depth":8},{"id":27,"text":"that her views of sex and gender were \" absolutist '' and `` incompatible with human dignity and fundamental rights of others . ''","depth":8},{"id":28,"text":"Forstater shared a copy of the judge 's ruling on Twitter .","depth":6},{"id":29,"text":"`` I struggle to express the shock and disbelief","depth":8},{"id":30,"text":"I feel","depth":9},{"id":31,"text":"at reading this judgment , ''","depth":9},{"id":32,"text":"she wrote .","depth":7},{"id":33,"text":"`` My belief","depth":9},{"id":34,"text":"as i set out in my witness statement","depth":9},{"id":35,"text":"is that sex is a biological fact","depth":9},{"id":36,"text":"& is immutable .","depth":9},{"id":37,"text":"There are two sexes .","depth":9},{"id":38,"text":"Men are male .","depth":11},{"id":39,"text":"Women are female .","depth":11},{"id":40,"text":"It is impossible to change sex .","depth":10},{"id":41,"text":"These were until very recently understood as basic facts of life . ''","depth":8},{"id":42,"text":"The researcher noted","depth":5},{"id":43,"text":"she will use `` preferred pronouns '' as a `` matter of courtesy ''","depth":6},{"id":44,"text":"and that everyone `` should be free to express themselves ,","depth":7},{"id":45,"text":"to break free of gender stereotypes","depth":8},{"id":46,"text":"and to live free of violence , harassment and discrimination . ''","depth":8},{"id":47,"text":"`` But this does not require removing people ' s freedom","depth":6},{"id":48,"text":"to speak about objective reality ,","depth":7},{"id":49,"text":"or to discuss proposed changes to law and to government policies clearly , ''","depth":7},{"id":50,"text":"she added .","depth":5},{"id":51,"text":"In a statement to Thursday , GLAAD 's head of talent Anthony Ramos condemned Rowling 's support for Forstater .","depth":5},{"id":52,"text":"`` J.K. Rowling ,","depth":10},{"id":53,"text":"whose books gave kids hope","depth":11},{"id":54,"text":"that they could work together","depth":12},{"id":55,"text":"to create a better world ,","depth":12},{"id":56,"text":"has now aligned herself with an anti-science ideology","depth":10},{"id":57,"text":"that denies the basic humanity of people","depth":11},{"id":58,"text":"who are transgender , ''","depth":11},{"id":59,"text":"he wrote .","depth":8},{"id":60,"text":"`` Trans men , trans women , and non-binary people are not a threat ,","depth":9},{"id":61,"text":"and to imply otherwise puts trans people at risk .","depth":9},{"id":62,"text":"Now is the time","depth":10},{"id":63,"text":"for allies","depth":12},{"id":64,"text":"who know and support trans people","depth":12},{"id":65,"text":"to speak up","depth":11},{"id":66,"text":"and support their fundamental right","depth":10},{"id":67,"text":"to be treated equally and fairly . ''","depth":10},{"id":68,"text":"Rowling 's tweet stirred controversy ,","depth":8},{"id":69,"text":"with some criticizing the author","depth":9},{"id":70,"text":"and others defending her .","depth":9},{"id":71,"text":"Among those","depth":10},{"id":72,"text":"criticizing her","depth":10},{"id":73,"text":"was the Human Rights Campaign ,","depth":9},{"id":74,"text":"which tweeted :","depth":9},{"id":75,"text":"\" Trans women are women .","depth":11},{"id":76,"text":"Trans men are men .","depth":12},{"id":77,"text":"Non-binary people are non-binary .","depth":12},{"id":78,"text":"CC :","depth":11},{"id":79,"text":"JK Rowling . \"","depth":11},{"id":80,"text":"J.K. Rowling says","depth":7},{"id":81,"text":"Dumbledore , Grindelwald had sexual relationship ;","depth":7},{"id":82,"text":"fans mourn missed opportunity","depth":6},{"id":83,"text":"`` This is incredibly disappointing to see , from someone","depth":8},{"id":84,"text":"whose writing espouses so much kindness , ''","depth":8},{"id":85,"text":"wrote @ LouisatheLast .","depth":7},{"id":86,"text":"`` Ms. Forstater has the right","depth":9},{"id":87,"text":"to think what she pleases ,","depth":9},{"id":88,"text":"but she does not have the right","depth":10},{"id":89,"text":"to expect","depth":11},{"id":90,"text":"that employers will always be okay with that .","depth":11},{"id":91,"text":"Trans people have to go to work too . '' `` As a gay man","depth":11},{"id":92,"text":"that found safety in Hogwarts throughout my childhood -","depth":11},{"id":93,"text":"knowing","depth":12},{"id":94,"text":"that Trans people wouldn ' t be able to have that safety","depth":12},{"id":95,"text":"breaks my heart , ''","depth":11},{"id":96,"text":"wrote user @ shahmiruk .","depth":7},{"id":97,"text":"More :","depth":4},{"id":98,"text":"'Harry Potter ' author JK Rowling gives $ 18.8 million gift for MS research","depth":4},{"id":99,"text":"Some Twitter users backed Rowling","depth":5},{"id":100,"text":"and slammed the criticism","depth":6},{"id":101,"text":"directed at her .","depth":6},{"id":102,"text":"`` The one time you say something reasonable","depth":7},{"id":103,"text":"and everyone ' s canceling you , ''","depth":7},{"id":104,"text":"wrote @ MsBlaireWhite .","depth":6},{"id":105,"text":"`` Just in case you needed any further proof","depth":8},{"id":106,"text":"that the Left is the party of raging intolerance , cancel culture , blind hypocrisy , and the full refusal","depth":9},{"id":107,"text":"to compromise on even the most reasonable of ideas outside their 'woke ' insanity ....","depth":9},{"id":108,"text":"here we are ,","depth":8},{"id":109,"text":"watching them cannibalize their own , ''","depth":8},{"id":110,"text":"wrote @ iheartmindy .","depth":6},{"id":111,"text":"J.K. Rowling mocks Trump with sarcasm :","depth":4},{"id":112,"text":"His Twitter rant is study of quiet strength","depth":4}],"relations":[{"parent":225,"left":163,"right":224,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":163,"left":135,"right":162,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":135,"left":133,"right":134,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":133,"left":128,"right":132,"relation":"context","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":128,"left":117,"right":127,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":117,"left":0,"right":116,"relation":"causal","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":116,"le